The models' key insight\'97that convergence holds without \uc0\u953  if r_a = r_b\'97enables riba-free designs, as premiums alone anchor prices. This supports financial innovations like DEX perpetuals, where proactive elimination of \u953  avoids usury while maintaining no-arbitrage. Empirical extensions (e.g., multifactor affine models) are suggested for estimation.\
