#### Detailed Derivations of Everlasting Options Proofs\
##### Theorem 6: General No-Arbitrage Pricing\
Assumptions: Continuous time; no-arbitrage (Q_a-martingale); payoff \uc0\u966 (x_t); dynamics df_\{o,t\} = [ - \u954 _\{o,t\} f_\{o,t\} + \u954 _\{o,t\} \u966 (x_t) ] dt + dM_t (M martingale); no-bubble (lim E [e^\{-\u8747  \u954 _o\} f_\{o,T\}] =0); integrability.\
